{"word":"G5236 - ὑπερβολή - hyperbolḗ - hoop-er-bol-ay' - Abundance","slug":"G5236","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑπερβολή</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>hyperbolḗ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>hoop-er-bol-ay'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Abundance"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C5;&#x0314;&#x03C0;&#x03B5;&#x03C1;&#x03B2;&#x03BF;&#x03BB;&#x03B7;&#x0301; - huperbole&#x0304;</b> - <i>hoop-er-bol-ay'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G5235\">G5235</a>; a <i>throwing beyond</i> others, that is, (figuratively) <i>supereminence</i>; adverbially (with <a href=\"#/G1519\">G1519</a> or <a href=\"#/G2596\">G2596</a>) <i>pre-eminently:</i> - abundance, (far more) exceeding, excellency, more excellent, beyond (out of) measure."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G5234\">G5234</a>, <a href=\"#/G5235\">G5235</a>"}]}